    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been meticulously maintained, serving as a dependable and comfortable ride. The engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and all major mechanical components are in solid working order. While the interior is clean and well-preserved, the exterior shows some very minor signs of normal use, such as small stone chips and light surface marks, but nothing that detracts from its overall attractive appearance. Buyers can expect a reliable, turn-key vehicle that is ready for many more miles of trouble-free driving.",
